Class WebDriverEncapsulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.arachnidium.core.WebDriverEncapsulation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDestroyable, IConfigurable, IConfigurationWrapper, org.openqa.selenium.internal.WrapsDriver

    public class WebDriverEncapsulation
extends Object
implements IDestroyable, IConfigurable, org.openqa.selenium.internal.WrapsDriver, IConfigurationWrapper
    This class creates an instance of required WebDriver implementor, wraps it and creates related components (WebdriverComponent)

        Parameters:
        supporteddriver - Is the one element from ESupportedDrivers enumeration which contains the class of required RemoteWebDriver subclass
        capabilities - in an instance of Capabilities
